OL,3,CMan who filmed himself 'pulling
OL,4,Cwheelies' in front of police appears
OL,5,Cin court
OL,7,FA Wiltshire motorcylist has been
OL,8,Fdisqualified from driving for a year
OL,9,Fafter pulling wheelies in front of
OL,10,Fpolice officers.
OL,12,FDamion Cregan, 23, of Cambridge Hill,
OL,13,FLarkhill, appeared at Salisbury
OL,14,FMagistrates Court on Thursday 28 March
OL,15,Fand pleaded guilty to dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving.
