OL,3,CMan who filmed himself 'pulling
OL,4,Cwheelies' in front of police appears
OL,5,Cin court
OL,7,FIt follows an incident at around
OL,8,F11.40am on 15 April 2023, near
OL,9,FBulford, where a motorcyclist failed
OL,10,Fto stop for police officers and then
OL,11,Ffilmed himself driving away.
OL,13,FCregan was disqualified from driving
OL,14,Ffor 12 months and was ordered to have
OL,15,Fan extended test. He was also ordered
OL,16,Fto carry out 300 hours of unpaid work,
OL,17,Fpay #85 costs and #114 surcharge.
