OL,3,CMan who filmed himself 'pulling
OL,4,Cwheelies' in front of police appears
OL,5,Cin court
OL,7,FPC Mike Hanscomb from the Road
OL,8,FPolicing Unit said: "When on patrol,
OL,9,Fwe were overtaken by a motorcyclist,
OL,10,Fwho did not have a number plate.
OL,12,F"When we asked him to pull over and
OL,13,Fstop he did not and started to do
OL,14,Fwheelies in front of the marked police
OL,15,Fcar.
OL,17,F"The driver also started to film
OL,18,Fhimself while driving at speed in a
OL,19,F30mph zone. This kind of behaviour is
OL,20,Ftotally unacceptable and put the
OL,21,Fpublic at great danger.
